- pick up items on fallen enemy ?



Responsibilities
----------------

Start Game
- needs to know game path to create directory

Setup Profile
- game path to find profiles
- towers when creating profile

Load Level
- current level number profile is on
- path to level file for loading
- profile for loading name, abilities into warrior

Load Player
- path to player directory for loading player

Play Level
- floor for playing unit turns
- level to know if won

Tally Score When Won
- warrior to know total score, new abilities, etc.
- floor to know if all enemies/captives are gone
- profile to add score, abilities to

Load Next Level
- next level number profile is on
- path to level file for loading
- profile for loading name, abilities into warrior

Next Level Generator
- profile to increment level and save.
- player path to generate next level directory
- template path or some way to generate readme
- previous level directory to copy player files from
